Package: khroma
Title: Colour Schemes for Archaeological Data Visualization
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Nicolas", "Frerebeau",
                  email = "nicolas.frerebeau@cea.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5759-4944"))
Description: Colour schemes for archaeological data visualization. Provides 
    Paul Tol's colour schemes and several thematic palettes (geologic timescale, 
    etc.) with scales for 'ggplot2'.
URL: http://github.com/nfrerebeau/khroma
BugReports: http://github.com/nfrerebeau/khroma/issues
